onsoundstart = (event) \f[B]=>\f[R] {};
.EE
.SH EVENT TYPE
A generic \f[CR]Event\f[R] with no added properties.
.SH EXAMPLES
You can use the \f[CR]soundstart\f[R] event in an
\f[CR]addEventListener\f[R] method:
